<div class='about-container'>
    <div class='row'>
        <div class='col-md-4'>
            <%# <img src='' width='300' alt='Profile Image' /> %>

            <%= image_tag "cloud_man.jpeg", width: '100%', alt: "Profile Image", class: 'about-img' %>

            <div class='skills'>
                <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                    <div class='skill'>
                        <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                        <div class='progress'>
                            <div
                                class='progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated bg-success'
                                role='progressbar'
                                style='width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%;'
                                aria-valuenow='<%= skill.percent_utilized %>'
                                aria-valuemin='0'
                                aria-valuemax='100'
                            >
                                <%= skill.percent_utilized %>% Utilized
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% end %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class='col-md-8'>
            <div class='about-card'>
                <div class='about-content'>
                    <h2>About Me</h2>
                    <hr class='w-75 mx-auto'>
                    <p class='about-description'>Hi! My name is Roman and I grew up in Utah, USA, mostly near the Salt Lake City area. I enjoy travelling, food, oceans, but mostly watching my boys do what they like to do. I learned some coding on my own when I was young and rediscovered my interest a few years ago. I'm now persuing skills that will hopefully lead me to a professional path in the tech world. So please feel free to <%= link_to 'contact me', contact_path%> if you'd like to work together or just to say hi.</p> 
                </div>
                <p>
                    <button
                        class='btn about-btn'
                        type='button'
                        data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                        data-bs-target='#projects'
                        aria-expanded='false'
                        aria-controls='projects'
                    >
                        Recent Projects
                    </button>

                    <button
                        class='btn about-btn'
                        type='button'
                        data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                        data-bs-target='#courses'
                        aria-expanded='false'
                        aria-controls='courses'
                    >
                        Recent Courses
                    </button>

                    <button
                        class='btn about-btn'
                        type='button'
                        data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                        data-bs-target='#socials'
                        aria-expanded='false'
                        aria-controls='socials'
                    >
                        Socials
                    </button>
                </p>

                <p>
                    <div class='collapse' id='projects'>
                        <div class='card card-block'>
                            <%= link_to "All my project", portfolios_path %>
                        </div>
                        <div class='card card-block'>
                            <a href='#' target='_blank'>Video Editing Portfolio Site</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class='card card-block'>
                            <a href="#" target='_blank'>Salon Website</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class='card card-block'>
                            <a href="#" target='_blank'>Personal Portfolio using ReactJs</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class='collapse' id='courses'>
                        <div class='card card-block'>
                            DevCamp Full Stack Development with Ruby on Rails
                        </div>
                        <div class='card card-block'>
                            React - The Complete Guide by Maximilian Schwarzmüller
                        </div>
                        <div class='card card-block'>
                            React Native - Practical Guide by Maximilian Schwarzmüller
                        </div>
                    </div>
                
                    <div class='collapse' id='socials'>
                        <div class='social-card card-block'>
                            <a href="https://github.com/Uthaeus" target="_blank"><%= fa_icon "github" %></a>
                            <a href="https://twitter.com/mjkisproblyagod" target="_blank"><%= fa_icon "twitter" %></a>
                            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/roman.lavery" target="_blank"><%= fa_icon "facebook" %></a>
                            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/roman-lavery-software-dev/" target="_blank"><%= fa_icon "linkedin" %></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
